<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-01-27T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-01-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="1403" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1403">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 819.77/144.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi><note n="2" xml:id="d1403fn2">A copy of this telegram was sent to the Secretary
                                of War on January 29.</note>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-01-27">
                                    <hi rend="italic">January 27, 1913</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Department’s January 21. Commission’s report to be forwarded tomorrow
                            recommends disapproval of contract especially on the <pb facs="1192" n="1088" xml:id="pg_1088"/> ground of indefiniteness of its
                            provisions which render impracticable proper consideration of its
                            technical merits.</p>
                        <p>Panaman President informs me that he will prolong for twenty days session
                            of Assembly.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Dodge</hi>.</signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>